      "description": "This car is in poor condition. It runs but has notable mechanical issues that will require attention. The exterior has significant cosmetic damage including dents, scratches, and possible rust. The interior is worn with visible damage to surfaces and components. Best suited for someone willing to invest in repairs or use it for parts.",
